---
layout: base.njk
title: "Key Terms & Concepts"
description: "Comprehensive glossary of UPSC key terms and concepts — definitions, explanations, etymology, and exam relevance for all GS papers."
---

<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span class="breadcrumb__sep">/</span>
      <a href="/resources/">Resources</a><span class="breadcrumb__sep">/</span>
      Key Terms & Concepts
    </nav>
    <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Resources</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">Key Terms & Concepts</h1>
    <p class="page-header__subtitle">Essential UPSC concepts explained in depth — with definitions, explanations, origins, and exam strategy for every term.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding:var(--space-8) 0;">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:var(--space-8); background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124,58,237,0.08), rgba(124,58,237,0.02)); border-left:4px solid #7c3aed;">
      <div class="article-body">
        <h3 style="color:#7c3aed; margin-bottom:var(--space-3);">How It Works</h3>
        <p>Every topic page on BharatNotes includes a <strong>Key Terms & Concepts</strong> section with comprehensive entries. Each entry includes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Pronunciation</strong> — IPA guide for confident usage</li>
          <li><strong>Definition & Explanation</strong> — Detailed, exam-oriented meaning</li>
          <li><strong>Etymology</strong> — Root word analysis for deeper understanding</li>
          <li><strong>Synonyms & Antonyms</strong> — With nuanced differences</li>
          <li><strong>UPSC Context</strong> — Paper, topic, and question patterns</li>
          <li><strong>Related Concepts</strong> — Interlinked for holistic preparation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:var(--text-2xl); color:var(--color-brand-dark); margin-bottom:var(--space-5); padding-bottom:var(--space-2); border-bottom:3px solid #7c3aed;">Browse by Subject</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom:var(--space-6);">Key Terms sections are embedded within each topic page. Browse subjects to find concept entries relevant to your study.</p>

    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:var(--space-5);">
      {% for s in subjects %}
      <a href="/subjects/{{ s.slug }}/" class="card" style="text-decoration:none; border-left:4px solid #7c3aed;">
        <span style="font-size:var(--text-2xl);">{{ s.icon }}</span>
        <h4 style="color:var(--color-brand-dark); margin:var(--space-2) 0;">{{ s.name }}</h4>
        <p class="card__desc">Explore key terms across {{ s.name }} topics.</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
